    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape, super reliable, and has been well-cared for since day one. Whether you\u2019re commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car is ready to go! Come check it out and take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 29900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
